CHANGES IN HICREP 1.5.0
1. added function to convert 3-column matrix to squared matrix
2. added function to extract data from .hic format

CHANGES IN hicrep 1.0.1:
1. Input format changed form N*(N+3) to N*N
2. prep function depcated
3. add function fast.mean.filter() that allows users to smooth the 
      matrix using a fast 2D filter algorithm
4. vignette file updated

CHANGES IN hicrep 0.99.0:
1. added unit tests
2. adjusted spaces for the source code
3. added some missing part in documentation


